body:
&nbsp;    
\* This mod __Fixes Elytra Deployment & Landing__, so that they work even with server lag. &nbsp;  
Every client modpack should have it. &nbsp;  

\- This mod only needs to be installed on the client-side, no special use actions needed, just use your Elytra normally and with confidence. &nbsp;  
```** Requires Forge version 2860+ on client-side, and is currently only for MC Java Edition 1.12.2  (1.18.2+ might come later if needed)```
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
Tired of your Elytra becoming a deathtrap when the server gets a little laggy?

This is the classic and essential Elytra Fix Module from MASA's Tweakeroo mod made into a Stand-alone Forge mod for Minecraft 1.12.2.

Unfortunately a lot of servers do not allow the Tweakeroo mod to be used because of some of its other features. &nbsp;  
This stand-alone Elytra-Fix mod will allow server owners and players to have the benefits of this essential fix without any of the controversy that comes with Tweakeroo's other features.
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
This mod retains the license used by Tweakeroo; LGPL 3.0.

Original Tweakeroo mod can be found at these links:

https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/tweakeroo &nbsp;  
https://masa.dy.fi/mcmods/client_mods/
